text: (Tyo yusuphako samipama ayo ra bhanna thalyo) yusupha! He satyanistha hamila'i (yasa sapanako artha) bhannus ki satavata moti ga'iharula'i satavata dubli ga'iharule kha'irakheka chan ra satavata baliharu hariya chan ra satavata sukeka jasabata ma manisaharuko samipama ga'i artha bhanu, hunasakcha ki tiniharule janun
